The paper discusses the use of machine learning in computational biology, specifically in the development of precision medicine. This topic falls under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG) as well as computational biology (cs.CB). The paper also touches on issues related to patient privacy, which could fall under the sub-categories of cryptography and security (cs.CR), databases (cs.DB), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
